<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract The article deals with the foundation of the University of Brasilia and Darcy Ribeiro's impact in it. It identifies three moments in the history of the University, corresponding to three different timings in the University's trajectory: utopia times, bureaucracy times, and dystopia times.]]></p></abstract>
